#: src/callback_func.c:514
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Frequency plots window closed: excitation type %d is incompatible.\n"
"Use type 0 (Applied E Field) or 5 (Current Discontinuity) instead."
msgstr ""
"Okno frekvenčných grafov zatvorené: typ budenia %d je nekompatibilný.\n"
"Použite namiesto toho typ 0 (Applied E Field) alebo 5 (Current "
"Discontinuity)."

#: src/callback_func.c:520
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Frequency plots are not available with excitation type %d.\n"
"This model uses Incident Field or Elementary Current Source excitation.\n"
"Change the EX card to type 0 (Applied E Field) or 5 (Current Discontinuity)."
msgstr ""
"Frekvenčné grafy nie sú dostupné s typom budenia %d.\n"
"Tento model používa budenie Incident Field alebo Elementary Current Source.\n"
"Zmeňte kartu EX na typ 0 (Applied E Field) alebo 5 (Current Discontinuity)."

