#: src/callbacks.c:137
msgid ""
"Ground plane detected in model. T_ant results will overcount ground effects. "
"Free-space models are standard for antenna temperature evaluation."
msgstr ""
"V modeli bola detegovaná zemná rovina. Výsledky T_ant nadhodnotia účinky "
"zeme. Pre vyhodnotenie teploty antény sú štandardom modely vo voľnom "
"priestore."

#: src/callbacks.c:153
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Max gain at θ=%.0f° (%.0f° from XY plane). Convention assumes beam in XY "
